{
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": {"type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --"},
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "description": "Métricas da aplicação coletadas via OpenTelemetry SDK seguindo as Semantic Conventions v1.x: requisições HTTP por rota/método, latências (P50/P99), taxa de erros HTTP, consultas ao banco de dados, contagem de threads/goroutines e profundidade de filas de mensagens. ATENÇÃO: os painéis exibem 'No data' até que a aplicação seja instrumentada com OTel SDK e configurada para enviar para otel-collector:4317 (gRPC) ou otel-collector:4318 (HTTP).",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "HTTP: Taxa de Requisições por Rota",
      "description": "Requisições por segundo agrupadas por rota HTTP e método. Permite ver quais endpoints são mais acessados e detectar picos de tráfego inesperados. Métrica OTel: http_server_request_duration_seconds_count (Semantic Convention HTTP).",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by(http_route, http_request_method) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count[5m]))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{http_request_method}} {{http_route}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"},
        "legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "max"]}
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0}
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "HTTP: Latência P50 e P99 por Rota",
      "description": "Latência de resposta HTTP no percentil 50 (mediana) e 99. P99 = 99% das requests respondem em X ms ou menos. Valores altos de P99 indicam casos extremos de lentidão mesmo quando a mediana parece normal. Métrica OTel: http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by(le, http_route) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "P50 {{http_route}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by(le, http_route) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "refId": "B",
          "legendFormat": "P99 {{http_route}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 5}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"},
        "legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "max"]}
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8}
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "HTTP: Taxa de Erros (4xx e 5xx)",
      "description": "Percentual de requisições HTTP com status de erro. 4xx = erro do cliente (ex: 404, 401, 400). 5xx = erro do servidor (ex: 500, 503). Uma taxa de 5xx crescente indica problema na aplicação; 4xx alto pode indicar clientes mal configurados ou endpoints inexistentes.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{http_response_status_code=~\"4..\"}[5m])) / sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count[5m])) * 100",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "Erros 4xx %"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{http_response_status_code=~\"5..\"}[5m])) / sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count[5m])) * 100",
          "refId": "B",
          "legendFormat": "Erros 5xx %"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 1},
              {"color": "red", "value": 5}
            ]
          },
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 20}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"},
        "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"}
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8}
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Banco de Dados: Duração das Operações P99",
      "description": "Latência P99 de operações no banco de dados, agrupadas por tipo de operação (SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE). Valores altos indicam queries lentas, índices ausentes ou sobrecarga do banco. Métrica OTel: db_client_operation_duration_seconds_bucket (Semantic Convention DB).",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by(le, db_operation_name) (rate(db_client_operation_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "P99 {{db_operation_name}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by(le, db_operation_name) (rate(db_client_operation_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "refId": "B",
          "legendFormat": "P50 {{db_operation_name}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 5}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"},
        "legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "max"]}
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 16}
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Banco de Dados: Taxa de Consultas por Operação",
      "description": "Número de operações no banco por segundo. Picos em UPDATE/DELETE durante horários inesperados podem indicar jobs agendados ou vazamentos de transação. Métrica OTel: db_client_operation_duration_seconds_count.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by(db_operation_name) (rate(db_client_operation_duration_seconds_count[5m]))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{db_operation_name}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"},
        "legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "max"]}
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 16}
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Threads / Goroutines Ativas",
      "description": "Número de threads (Java/C#) ou goroutines (Go) em execução. Crescimento contínuo sem estabilização indica vazamento de threads (thread leak) — threads são criadas mas não destruídas. Para Go: process_runtime_go_goroutines. Para JVM: jvm_threads_current. Para .NET: process_thread_count.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "process_runtime_go_goroutines",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "Goroutines (Go) - {{job}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "jvm_threads_current",
          "refId": "B",
          "legendFormat": "Threads (JVM) - {{job}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "process_thread_count",
          "refId": "C",
          "legendFormat": "Threads (.NET) - {{job}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"},
        "legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"]}
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 24}
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Fila de Mensagens: Mensagens Publicadas e Processadas",
      "description": "Taxa de mensagens publicadas e consumidas em filas (RabbitMQ, Kafka, SQS, etc.). A diferença entre publicadas e processadas indica acúmulo na fila (backpressure). Se a fila cresce indefinidamente, os consumers não acompanham os producers. Métrica OTel: messaging_client_published_messages_total e messaging_receive_duration_seconds_count (Semantic Convention Messaging).",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by(messaging_system, messaging_destination_name) (rate(messaging_client_published_messages_total[5m]))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "Publicadas - {{messaging_system}}/{{messaging_destination_name}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum by(messaging_system, messaging_destination_name) (rate(messaging_receive_duration_seconds_count[5m]))",
          "refId": "B",
          "legendFormat": "Processadas - {{messaging_system}}/{{messaging_destination_name}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"},
        "legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "max"]}
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 24}
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 41,
  "tags": ["observability", "application", "http", "database", "messaging"],
